          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/26350851/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/26350851/" class="">第4页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/yce/" class=" " title="嵇嘉理">嵇嘉理</a>
                (封海了，皮皮虾秋天见)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="26350851">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">在革命党眼里，立宪派一向是比大清朝廷更加危险的敌人：他们反对革命，就是“顽固不化的反动派”；他们支持革命，就是“投机取巧的阴谋家”。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-05-13 21:16</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>在革命党眼里，立宪派一向是比大清朝廷更加危险的敌人：他们反对革命，就是“顽固不化的反动派”；他们支持革命，就是“投机取巧的阴谋家”。</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







